snippet.title: PLS DO NOT CLICK THE SOUND EVER 😭
snippet.description:
#shorts #english #usa #architecture 

This is what the final exam for a group of architecture students looked like.
They had to build a tower capable of holding different weights using only wooden sticks.

After days of preparation, when they finally finished, their professor made an interesting announcement: if even one tower could support the dumbbells without collapsing, the entire class would instantly earn the highest grade.

Everyone was super excited… but there was a problem. One after another, the towers failed, since almost nobody had paid attention in class. Some towers were obviously too weak—the structures were too thin and lacked the strength of the triangle design.

Finally, there was only one student left, and the professor was already convinced no one would pass.

But when the dumbbells hit the last tower, it held strong—giving the entire class top grades.

Credits to ballstatecap via Instagram!
